{"title":"香菜观察日记","slug":"growing-coriander-diary","date":"2021-08-15T11:26:05.000Z","updated":"2021-09-05T14:38:53.365Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/growing-coriander-diary.json","realPath":"/2021/08/15/growing-coriander-diary/","excerpt":"我种下一颗种子，终于长出了果实，今天是个伟大日子。<br>摘下香菜炒个蛋，摘下香菜煲个汤，让香菜每天为你甜蜜。","covers":["https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193431.jpg","https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193457.jpg","https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193521.jpg","https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210820000445.jpg","https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210821210653.jpg","https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210826011732.jpg","https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210826011747.jpg","https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210830205209.jpg","https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210905223653.jpg"],"cover":"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193055.jpg","content":"<p>我种下一颗种子，终于长出了果实，今天是个伟大日子。<br>摘下香菜炒个蛋，摘下香菜煲个汤，让香菜每天为你甜蜜。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p><strong>2021.08.14</strong></p>\n<p>今天是个下雨的七夕劫，适合“播种”。女朋友送了几包香菜种子，还有来自长白山的泥土。我将用我的勤劳的双手，将它们变成香菜炒蛋。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193431.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">装备</span></p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193457.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">松土</span></p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193521.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">播种</span></p>\n<p>就这么简单，欲知后事如何，咱们下期再会。</p>\n<p><strong>2021.08.19</strong></p>\n<p>这两天参加公司训练营，每天早出晚归，无暇在人间逗留。今晚无意瞥到香菜苗苗居然 🌱 了，可喜可贺。By the way，小伙伴们很给力</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210820000445.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">🌱</span></p>\n<p><strong>2021.08.21</strong></p>\n<p>今天已经长成小苗苗了，炒一碗香菜苗。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210821210653.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">小苗苗</span></p>\n<p><strong>2021.08.26</strong></p>\n<p>这两天海豹训练营太卷了，每天肝到十二点，只能让你暗里生长了。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210826011732.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">暗里</span></p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210826011747.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">生长</span></p>\n<p><strong>2021.08.30</strong></p>\n<p>这两天杭州太热了，一直给她放阳台晒，感觉晒萎了。赶紧拿到空调间吹吹空调，似乎还能抢救一下。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210830205209.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">萎了</span></p>\n<p><strong>2021.09.05</strong></p>\n<p>尘归尘，土归土，香菜终究要归土。周末去菜市场买点香菜，炒个蛋，以祭奠香菜宝宝们的在天之灵。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210905223653.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">任务终了</span></p>\n","more":"<p><strong>2021.08.14</strong></p>\n<p>今天是个下雨的七夕劫，适合“播种”。女朋友送了几包香菜种子，还有来自长白山的泥土。我将用我的勤劳的双手，将它们变成香菜炒蛋。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193431.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">装备</span></p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193457.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">松土</span></p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210815193521.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">播种</span></p>\n<p>就这么简单，欲知后事如何，咱们下期再会。</p>\n<p><strong>2021.08.19</strong></p>\n<p>这两天参加公司训练营，每天早出晚归，无暇在人间逗留。今晚无意瞥到香菜苗苗居然 🌱 了，可喜可贺。By the way，小伙伴们很给力</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210820000445.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">🌱</span></p>\n<p><strong>2021.08.21</strong></p>\n<p>今天已经长成小苗苗了，炒一碗香菜苗。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210821210653.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">小苗苗</span></p>\n<p><strong>2021.08.26</strong></p>\n<p>这两天海豹训练营太卷了，每天肝到十二点，只能让你暗里生长了。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210826011732.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">暗里</span></p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210826011747.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">生长</span></p>\n<p><strong>2021.08.30</strong></p>\n<p>这两天杭州太热了，一直给她放阳台晒，感觉晒萎了。赶紧拿到空调间吹吹空调，似乎还能抢救一下。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210830205209.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">萎了</span></p>\n<p><strong>2021.09.05</strong></p>\n<p>尘归尘，土归土，香菜终究要归土。周末去菜市场买点香菜，炒个蛋，以祭奠香菜宝宝们的在天之灵。</p>\n<p><img  src=\"https://pic.izhaoo.com/20210905223653.jpg\"  ><span class=\"image-caption\">任务终了</span></p>","categories":[{"name":"随笔","path":"api/categories/随笔.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"